                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7003" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0165</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7577 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">凤栖山村：宏图劳务的产业惠农</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Phoenix lands on the Country: An Industry that Benefits Farmers of Hongtu Labor Service Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">黄昶生，吕成，崔杨，李欣悦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（华东）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">青岛宏图人力资源有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业惠农；精准扶贫；企业社会责任；利益相关者；可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">industries benefiting farmers；targeted poverty alleviation; corporate social responsibility; stakeholder; sustainable development</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">在乡村振兴和共同富裕的道路上，青岛宏图人力资源服务有限公司贡献了一份力量，该公司本是一家传统的劳务派遣公司，经过十几年的发展，公司规模日益壮大，总经理吴志刚不忘初心，依托其生产外包业务中积累的产业经验，积极筹划布局精准扶贫项目——乡村惠民工厂，帮助农村的老人和妇女在家门口脱贫致富，并将该模式成功复制到周边的乡村，吸引大波青年“回流”，改善村容村貌，实现了模式可复制的乡村振兴发展新业态，形成与农村劳动力、订单企业三方共赢的利益联合体。本案例通过强调宏图劳务响应国家政策、设立并经营乡村惠民工厂、助力乡村振兴，实现企业社会共同繁荣，帮助学习者了解、掌握企业社会责任的内涵与特征、利益相关者、企业可持续发展等知识，能够对有意愿践行产业扶贫的企业提供经验与启发。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Qingdao Hongtu Human Resources Service Co., Ltd. is a traditional labor dispatch company. With the growing scale of the company, general manager Wu Zhigang has not forgotten his original intention and actively undertakes corporate social responsibility. Relying on the industrial experience accumulated in its production outsourcing business, it actively planned and arranged the poverty alleviation project, rural people&#39;s welfare factory, helped rural women get rid of poverty and became rich at the door of their home, and successfully replicated the model to the surrounding villages, improved the appearance of villages, realized the new business form of Rural Revitalization and development with replicable model, and formed a win-win interest consortium with rural labor force and order enterprises. By emphasizing that rural people&#39;s welfare factory has undertaken corporate social responsibility and contributed to rural revitalization, this case realizes the common prosperity of the enterprise society by emphasizing that Hongtu 
Labor responds to national policies, sets up and operates rural factories that benefit the people, and helps rural revitalization, and helps learners understand and master the connotation and characteristics of corporate social responsibility, stakeholders, enterprise sustainable development and other knowledge.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》、《企业伦理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者理论；合作共赢理念；价值共创理论；企业社会责任与战略性企业社会责任；企业社会责任与企业可持续发展</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
